{
  "texts": [
    "However, jailbreak prompts do not work for every malicious query.",
    "Experiments by Deng et al. [7] show that even with jailbreak prompts, the success rate of jailbreaking GPT-4 is only 15.32%.",
    "In this study, we use jailbreak prompts by automatically constructing high-quality malicious queries and appending them to the prompts.",
    "This causes the LLM to generate toxic content.",
    "Knowledge DistillationKnowledge distillation is a pivotal technique in machine learning."
  ]
}